---
title: Creamy Mushroom & Truffle Fettuccine with Tomato-Rocket Salad
description: This fettuccine dish pairs the earthy flavour of mushroom and truffle with an easy creamy sauce. The side salad
balances the richness of the pasta with peppery rocket and sharp Parmesan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65276f00fe6b58e2f98e215b-b2e8249d.jpeg
